INTRODUCTION
ART is a company established in pursuit of the vision of a group of European leading figures in the global motor sport industry who, in cooperation with their Chinese partners, wish to assist and be part of establishing China as a leading nation in the world of motorsports. This will take place trough the localization and institutionalization of knowledge and expertise. Upon completion of the necessary preparatory and intermediate phases, the ultimate goal of ART, its employees and associates, is to successfully compete in Formula One – the pinnacle of motorsports.
 
In the first year, successful candidates will undergo an intensive training in general motorsport technical knowledge. These candidates will then specialise in the various profiles that a fully developed motorsports industry will require. That specialisation will have a unique moment in Europe during a 9 months working period inside one of ART’s associated companies. It will then be matured through personal experience in the following years working on race-car and engine projects in China.
 
If you are hungry to learn from the undisputed leaders of the industry, if you have an indomitable spirit when faced with challenges, if you possess a pioneering spirit and enjoy the creative process, we would like to hear from you.
 
 
